ium text-slate-700\">Click to upload or drag file here</p><p class=\"mt-0.5 text-xs text-slate-500\">PDF, PNG, JPG — max 5MB</p></div></div></div></div><div><label class=\"mb-2 block text-sm font-medium text-slate-700\">Letter of Intent<!-- --> <span class=\"text-red-500\">*</span></label><div class=\"relative rounded-xl border-2 border-dashed px-5 py-5 transition border-slate-300 bg-slate-50 hover:border-[#0B1F3A]\"><input type=\"file\" accept=\".pdf,.png,.jpg,.jpeg\" class=\"absolute inset-0 cursor-pointer opacity-0\"/><div class=\"flex items-center gap-4\"><div class=\"flex h-10 w-10 shrink-0 items-center justify-center rounded-lg bg-slate-200 text-slate-500\"><svg class=\"h-5 w-5\" fill=\"none\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\"><path stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" d=\"M4 16v1a3 3 0 003 3h10a3 3 0 003-3v-1m-4-8l-4-4m0 0L8 8m4-4v12\"></path></svg></div><div class=\"min-w-0\"><p class=\"truncate text-sm font-medium text-slate-700\">Click to upload or drag file here</p><p class=\"mt-0.5 text-xs text-slate-500\">PDF, PNG, JPG — max 5MB</p></div></div></div></div><div class=\"grid gap-4\"><div><label class=\"mb-2 block text-sm font-medium text-slate-700\">Payment Proof Screenshot — INR 3,200 (non-refundable)<!-- --> <span class=\"text-red-500\">*</span></label><div class=\"relative rounded-xl border-2 border-dashed px-5 py-5 transition border-slate-300 bg-slate-50 hover:border-[#0B1F3A]\"><input type=\"file\" accept=\".pdf,.png,.jpg,.jpeg\" class=\"absolute inset-0 cursor-pointer opacity-0\"/><div class=\"flex items-center gap-4\"><div class=\"flex h-10 w-10 shrink-0 items-center justify-center rounded-lg bg-slate-200 text-slate-500\"><svg class=\"h-5 w-5\" fill=\"none\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\"><path stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" d=\"M4 16v1a3 3 0 003 3h10a3 3 0 003-3v-1m-4-8l-4-4m0 0L8 8m4-4v12\"></path></svg></div><div class=\"min-w-0\"><p class=\"truncate text-sm font-medium text-slate-700\">Click to upload or drag file here</p><p class=\"mt-0.5 text-xs text-slate-500\">PDF, PNG, JPG — max 5MB</p></div></div></div></div><div><label class=\"mb-2 block text-sm font-medium text-slate-700\">UPI / Bank Transaction Reference ID <span class=\"text-red-500\">*</span></label><input required=\"\" placeholder=\"e.g. 318492857364 or UPI Ref No.\" class=\"w-full rounded-xl border border-slate-300 bg-white px-4 py-3 text-sm outline-none transition focus:border-[#0B1F3A] focus:ring-2 focus:ring-[#0B1F3A]/10\" value=\"\"/><p class=\"mt-1.5 text-xs text-slate-500\">Enter the exact transaction or UPI reference number from your payment confirmation. The IEC will cross-verify this with bank records.</p></div></div></div></section><div class=\"rounded-2xl border border-amber-200 bg-amber-50 p-6\"><p class=\"text-sm leading-7 text-amber-900\"><strong>Declaration:</strong> By submitting this form, I confirm that all information and documents provided are accurate and genuine. I understand that false declarations, fraudulent documents, falsified payment references, or incomplete submissions will result in immediate disqualification and further IEC disciplinary action.</p></div><div class=\"flex justify-end\"><button type=\"submit\" class=\"rounded-xl bg-[#0B1F3A] px-10 py-4 text-sm font-semibold text-white transition hover:bg-[#153E75] disabled:cursor-not-allowed disabled:opacity-60\">Submit Official Application</button></div></form></div></main><!--$--><!--/$--></main><footer class=\"border-t bg-white\"><div class=\"mx-auto max-w-7xl px-6 py-6\"><div class=\"flex flex-col gap-2 text-sm text-slate-500 md:flex-row md:items-center md:justify-between\"><p>© 2026 Independent Elections Commission (IEC) — ALSI</p><p>Official Election Registration Platform</p></div></div></footer></div><script src=\"/_next/static/chunks/03tfhzrunrhlw.js\" id=\"_R_\" async=\"\"></script><script>(self.__next_f=self.__next_f||[]).push([0])</script><script>self.__n